headline: CDW to Announce Second Quarter 2025 Results on August 6
summary: VERNON HILLS, Ill., July 23, 2025--CDW Corporation (Nasdaq: CDW) announced today that it will host a webcast conference call to discuss its second quarter 2025 results on Wednesday, August 6, 2025, at 7:30 a.m. CT/8:30 a.m. ET.
